column5: This year's Tourney winner is Team 5 - The Crank Mates.  Congratulations Team 5    1st Place - Team 5  2nd Place - Team 7  3rd Place - Team 4  4th Place - Team 8  5th Place - Team 2  6th Place - Team 6  7th Place - Team 1  8th Place - Team 3
Congrats to Team 5!! Nice fish in all categories is impressive.
Well done Team 5….very impressive catches indeed…….52" MUSKY?!??!!!!
Good job team 5...  Hey.  Queen!  At least we didn't get last!!
Congrats team 5  Sorry team 2 for not using my sign on bigger cats or musky.
Not your fault Mike, I doubt you'd be able to add that many inches with just those 2 fish haha. Congrats to team 5, hope to see you all again next year!

First off,,,,,,,,,,,,,,  A BIG THANKS TO YOU J FOR TAKING THE TIME TO KEEP IT ALL TOGETHER.  GREAT JOB.  Team 5,congrats. Nice numbers.  Team 7 nice runner up. Glad I was able to get that elusive whitie that some didnt.LOL  Again GREAT JOB DONE BY ALL
Can someone post pics of the winning species?
Thanks Joey for all your hard work, and the captains too. It was a fun tourney, as always. That's a heck of year team 5 had
Thanks Joey.... Great year...  Ron kinda piggy backed the team this year.... Lol  Great year Ron and great year team 5...

A special thanks to Joey for taking the time to put this on. Spiel was a great captain and we also had some great team members on our side!  Cheers, Ron...

Next year Ron gets a 45 inch penalty for to much time to fish lol. Thanks to everyone Captains and Joey for donating a lot of their time to make this possible. I am happy to see a lot of people participating in this fun event.    Art
Thanks for doing the tourney this year Joey.  Team 5: We call us the Ron and Mike show.  (My perch helped)
I Cant wait to join in next year !
thanks for doing the tournament Joey, congratulations team 5
Ron??? What?? LOL  thanks Joey for everything!!!!  Congrats team 5
